{"tid":2201521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［笑話一則］聶德權：普及社區檢測參與人數達設立目標","createTime":"2020-09-14T00:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T07:26:57.000Z","uid":277339,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a609d4c5a294f286a2b93026047f2ddf49bf2569","tid":2201521,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:38:18.000Z","msg":"普及社區檢測計劃推行最後一天，公務員事務局長聶德權在本台節目表示，截至昨晚8時，有171.9萬名市民已經接受採樣；昨日有5.3萬人採樣，當中3.4萬人並無預約登記。他表示，連同今日已經預約的萬幾人，參與數字已達到計劃的目標，了解到社區感染情況。 <br />\n<br />\n聶德權說，計劃的陽性比例反映，現時疫情已經到「水尾」，不過未「斷尾」，而且確診個案遍及社區不同層面，即是社區有廣泛傳播鏈，加上昨日新增確診個案數字略為回升，繼續有感染源頭不明個案，令人關注疫情會否反彈<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2357053&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8BD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=f4abc553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357053</a>"},{"pid":"036220cd4e33ec16dfc05cc77b50e8722a064d45","tid":2201521,"uid":55043,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:40:08.000Z","msg":"又話冇目標既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec514aee7c3cd66170636ea339eacda57fcd9768","tid":2201521,"uid":57532,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:44:07.000Z","msg":"唔係500萬咩？"},{"pid":"5ee97edd7ecc255419c70a27a922673b9911c212","tid":2201521,"uid":32028,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"036220cd4e33ec16dfc05cc77b50e8722a064d45","tid":2201521,"uid":55043,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:40:08.000Z","msg":"又話冇目標既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:45:02.000Z","msg":"就係無目標, 完左先可以話完成目標, 港共最鐘意搬龍門"},{"pid":"c5120d090ad07dca2e2e5cb8c90e539f00f39ec0","tid":2201521,"uid":92697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:50:34.000Z","msg":"百幾萬次嘅data去了解7百幾萬人口嘅data<br />\n仲話達標 <br